{"tid":1396832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連各大公司都預計5/8交通有困難，叫員工返唔到唔好返，社會有哂心理準備會癱瘓，有班人反而叫人唔好塞鐵？","createTime":"2019-08-02T08:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:20:07.000Z","uid":31215,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc280c1049f5566762fcc42f420a96c86626995d","tid":1396832,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"好多人唔肯罷工，係因為驚有手尾<br />\n既然好多公司都預啲員工未必返到，手尾少左<br />\n連登仔就索性癱瘓全港助攻啦，交通唔受阻，好多人都冇藉口架啦<br />\n今次係咁多次不合作運動之中預告得最好嘅一次，社會有哂心理準備，做哂危機管理，唔好今次先黎縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5/8要七區集會，癱瘓全線地鐵，路面擠塞<br />\n<br />\n呼籲連登仔七點半同我一齊去地鐵搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5729d156b9c89bc951cb6d32d87e29c632cab6b5","tid":1396832,"uid":129243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"講真返唔到工 都要局住放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe8c1dc32feb4409b9deee43701e99627d3182a","tid":1396832,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5729d156b9c89bc951cb6d32d87e29c632cab6b5","tid":1396832,"uid":129243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"講真返唔到工 都要局住放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"罷到工嘅主動罷<br />\n罷唔到嘅被動罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876764ea43d55afb339432b19956ebdef0cbe93f","tid":1396832,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4099d1cdf1e6f0955a7003e337a8c68b7889c9","tid":1396832,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"塞埋九龍塘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji